WEBVTT

00:01.802 --> 00:03.537
HEY, DID MY MOM CALL?

00:03.537 --> 00:06.307
NO, I THOUGHT
SHE CARPOOLED WITH YOU TODAY.

00:06.307 --> 00:09.643
OH, SHE DID, BUT SHE LIT
A CIGARETTE IN THE CAR AGAIN,

00:09.643 --> 00:12.146
SO I PULLED OVER,
AND I KICKED HER OUT.

00:12.146 --> 00:14.215
YOU LEFT YOUR MOM
IN THE STREET?

00:14.215 --> 00:17.351
NO, I SLOWED DOWN
SO SHE COULD GET BACK IN.

00:17.351 --> 00:19.620
THEN WHEN SHE GOT CLOSE,
I SPED UP AGAIN.

00:19.620 --> 00:22.856
THEN I SLOWED DOWN,
THEN I SPED UP.

00:22.856 --> 00:26.660
HEY, TELL HER ABOUT WHEN
YOUR MOM DOVE FOR THE BUMPER,

00:26.660 --> 00:30.331
RIGHT WHEN YOU HIT THE BRAKES,
IT WAS LIKE, BOOM! POW!

00:30.331 --> 00:31.932
THAT WAS ACCIDENTAL,

00:31.932 --> 00:34.034
BUT VERY FUNNY.

00:34.034 --> 00:35.369
(laughs)

00:35.369 --> 00:37.338
GEORGE,
SOME GUY CALLED FOR YOU.

00:37.338 --> 00:40.241
HE SAID HE WAS ONE
OF YOUR MOM'S BOYFRIENDS?

00:40.241 --> 00:42.243
WELL,
THAT COULD BE ANYBODY.

00:42.243 --> 00:45.246
I MEAN, MY MOM WAS
THE FAST FOOD OF DATING--

00:45.246 --> 00:47.481
EASY, CHEAP AND PERFECT
WHEN YOU'RE DRUNK.

00:47.481 --> 00:51.452
HEY, YEAH, SHE WAS THE FIRST ONE
WITH THE DOLLAR MENU.

00:51.452 --> 00:53.354
(laughs)

00:54.922 --> 00:57.425
HE SAID HIS NAME
IS WAYNE HILL?

00:57.425 --> 00:59.460
WAYNE HILL. OH, MAN!

00:59.460 --> 01:02.196
WELL, HE SAID HE'S SINGLE NOW,
AND HE'S COMING OVER

01:02.196 --> 01:05.899
TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT BENNY.
AGAIN? I WISH THAT GUY WOULD
STOP TRYING TO USE ME

01:05.899 --> 01:09.002
TO SMOOTH THINGS OVER WITH HER.
WELL, THEN JUST GIVE HIM
YOUR MOM'S NUMBER.

01:09.002 --> 01:12.206
NO WAY. I'M NOT LETTING THAT GUY
ANYWHERE NEAR HER.

01:12.206 --> 01:15.176
I EVEN TOLD HIM
SHE LOST HER JOB AT THE FACTORY

01:15.176 --> 01:17.178
SO HE WOULDN'T TRY
TO CALL HER THERE.

01:17.178 --> 01:20.981
WHAT DID HE DO TO HER?
BROKE HER HEART, OR WHATEVER
SHE HAS THAT PUMPS BLOOD,

01:20.981 --> 01:22.983
TEQUILA AND ACID
THROUGH HER VEINS.

01:22.983 --> 01:24.885
YOU WERE THERE. REMEMBER?

01:24.885 --> 01:30.090
(imitating gunfire)

01:31.892 --> 01:33.827
OH. (laughs)

01:33.827 --> 01:36.063
(laughs) STOP. OH.

01:36.063 --> 01:38.666
GEORGE,
TAKE YOUR GIRLFRIEND

01:38.666 --> 01:40.868
AND GO PLAY DOLLS
SOMEPLACE ELSE.

01:43.604 --> 01:44.872
THEY'RE NOT DOLLS.

01:44.872 --> 01:48.809
THEY'RE G.I.s,
AND THEY'RE KICKING HIPPIE ASS.

01:48.809 --> 01:50.211
GOTTA GO, BABE.

01:50.211 --> 01:53.381
I GOTTA BE UP EARLY TO FILM
A COMMERCIAL FOR THE NEW STORE.

01:53.381 --> 01:55.583
OH, I FINALLY
HOOKED A WINNER.

01:55.583 --> 01:58.319
YOU ARE THE RENT-TO-OWN
FURNITURE KING.

01:58.319 --> 02:00.321
WELL, YOU KNOW
WHAT THEY SAY--

02:00.321 --> 02:02.890
"BEHIND EVERY GOOD MAN,
THERE'S A GOOD WOMAN...

02:02.890 --> 02:06.394
AND QUALITY FURNITURE
FOR JUST PENNIES A MONTH."

02:06.394 --> 02:08.696
UNLESS, OF COURSE,
YOU MISS A PAYMENT.

02:08.696 --> 02:10.931
THEN I JACK UP
THE INTEREST 30%.

02:10.931 --> 02:12.566
OH.
SUCKERS.

02:12.566 --> 02:16.237
OH, DON'T TALK LIKE THAT
IF YOU HAVE TO LEAVE.

02:16.237 --> 02:18.071
(laughs)

02:18.071 --> 02:21.275
HEY, NEW WATER BEDS COMING IN.
MAYBE I'LL GET YOU ONE.

02:21.275 --> 02:23.644
(Benny squeals)
YOU, TOO, LITTLE MAN.

02:23.644 --> 02:26.680
OH, HE MAKES
HIS OWN WATER BED EVERY NIGHT.

02:26.680 --> 02:28.816
MOM!

02:30.984 --> 02:32.786
WHAT'S THAT?

02:32.786 --> 02:33.787
WHAT?

02:33.787 --> 02:35.856
HELLO.

02:35.856 --> 02:38.892
THERE'S SOMETHING
FALLING OUT OF YOUR POCKET.

02:38.892 --> 02:42.396
WHAT THE HELL?

02:45.666 --> 02:49.637
YEAH. WHAT THE HELL
WAS THAT DOING IN THERE?

02:49.637 --> 02:53.106
BENNY, I SWEAR, I'VE NEVER
SEEN THIS BEFORE IN MY LIFE.

02:53.106 --> 02:54.708
YOU'RE CHEATING ON ME,
AREN'T YOU?

02:54.708 --> 02:57.211
(imitates Rodney Dangerfield)
HEY, THOSE THINGS ARE SO BIG,

02:57.211 --> 03:01.181
I'LL BE THERE'LL STILL BE SNOW
ON THEM IN THE SUMMER. HEY.

03:02.583 --> 03:05.719
(normal voice) HE'S A GUY ON TV.
NOBODY RESPECTS HIM.

03:07.187 --> 03:10.391
MY MOM WAS DEPRESSED FOR A MONTH
AFTER WAYNE CHEATED ON HER.

03:10.391 --> 03:13.394
THAT'S WHY I DON'T EVEN
TELL HER WHEN HE CALLS.

03:13.394 --> 03:16.564
THAT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.
MAYBE HE'S CHANGED.

03:16.564 --> 03:17.931
ANGIE, GUYS DON'T CHANGE.

03:17.931 --> 03:20.368
YOU'VE BEEN TRYING
TO CHANGE ME FOR YEARS,

03:20.368 --> 03:22.603
BUT I STILL SCOOP
THE PEANUT BUTTER OUT

03:22.603 --> 03:26.173
WITH MY FINGERS.
NO, YOU DON'T. I CHECK.

03:26.173 --> 03:29.543
OH, I DO. I JUST SMOOTH IT
WITH A SPOON SO YOU CAN'T TELL.

03:29.543 --> 03:32.045
IF YOU ALREADY
HAVE THE SPOON OUT,

03:32.045 --> 03:33.847
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST USE THAT?

03:33.847 --> 03:36.517
BECAUSE IT TASTES BETTER
OFF MY FINGER.

03:36.517 --> 03:38.752
IT'S SCARY, REALLY,
HOW LITTLE YOU KNOW.

03:38.752 --> 03:40.488
(doorbell rings)

03:40.488 --> 03:42.890
THAT'S PROBABLY WAYNE.

03:44.625 --> 03:47.160
YOU BETTER NOT TELL WHAT
REALLY HAPPENED WITH WAYNE.

03:47.160 --> 03:48.829
I WON'T.

03:48.829 --> 03:52.199
NO, YOU KNOW WHAT? IT'D BE SAFER
IF YOU JUST GOT OUT OF HERE.

03:52.199 --> 03:55.503
NAH, YOU CAN TRUST ME.
I CAN KEEP A SECRET.
NO, YOU CAN'T.

03:55.503 --> 03:58.639
YOU'VE NEVER BEEN ABLE TO KEEP
A SECRET YOUR WHOLE LIFE. OUT.

03:58.639 --> 04:01.041
OH, YEAH?
I DIDN'T TELL YOU THAT

04:01.041 --> 04:03.611
THAT GUY AT WORK,
"DRILL PRESS" STEVE, IS GAY.

04:03.611 --> 04:05.879
