HE STOCKS THE VENDING MACHINES,

04:05.879 --> 04:08.081
YET THEY CALL HIM
"DRILL PRESS STEVE."

04:08.081 --> 04:09.917
THINK. THINK.

04:09.917 --> 04:13.220
AHEM. GEORGE.

04:13.220 --> 04:15.689
HEY, GEORGE.
YOU LOOK GOOD.

04:15.689 --> 04:17.625
