LAST TIME,

04:32.873 --> 04:35.843
MY MOM'S NOT GONNA SEE YOU,
MAN, SO GIVE IT UP.

04:35.843 --> 04:38.546
YOU KNOW, IF I'M GONNA GET
TURNED DOWN AGAIN,

04:38.546 --> 04:41.582
