TO COME CLEAN.

09:03.577 --> 09:06.179
AND THEN
SHE SET HIM ON FIRE?

09:06.179 --> 09:09.182
QUE LA, WHAT ABOUT THE ONE
WHERE THE WIFE IS RIGHT,

09:09.182 --> 09:11.885
BUT SHE'S SO ANNOYING,
THAT WHEN SHE GOES MISSING,

09:11.885 --> 09:13.887
