09:13.887 --> 09:16.890
IT'S SAD, BUT I FOUND MYSELF
ROOTING FOR THE HUSBAND.

09:18.759 --> 09:22.162
ALL I HEARD WAS,
"THE WIFE IS RIGHT."

09:31.639 --> 09:34.241
HEY, HEY,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING? HEY.

09:34.241 --> 09:35.643
OKAY.

09:37.911 --> 09:41.348
WE GOTTA TALK
ABOUT SOMETHING. OKAY?

09:41.348 --> 09:44.818
REMEMBER A LONG TIME AGO
YOU HAD THIS BOYFRIEND,

09:44.818 --> 09:46.253
THIS GUY NAMED WAYNE?

09:46.253 --> 09:49.657
OF COURSE I REMEMBER WAYNE.
(chuckles)

09:49.657 --> 09:53.694
HE WAS THE BEST GUY
I EVER WENT OUT WITH,

09:53.694 --> 09:56.764
UNTIL, YOU KNOW,
HE CHEATED ON ME.

09:56.764 --> 10:00.200
WAIT, YOU LIKED HIM
THAT MUCH, HUH?

10:00.200 --> 10:03.871
OH, I WAITED FOREVER
FOR HIM TO MAKE IT UP TO ME,

10:03.871 --> 10:06.707
BUT HE NEVER DID.

10:06.707 --> 10:08.709
IT'S ONE OF
MY BIGGEST DISAPPOINTMENTS.

10:08.709 --> 10:12.746
PROBABLY, HE WOULD'VE
CHANGED MY LIFE FOREVER.

10:12.746 --> 10:14.948
WHY DO YOU BRING HIM UP?

10:17.617 --> 10:19.687
UM...

10:19.687 --> 10:22.690
HE'S DEAD.

10:22.690 --> 10:24.992
I JUST THOUGHT
THAT YOU SHOULD KNOW.

10:24.992 --> 10:29.697
WELL, HE'S PROBABLY NOT
GONNA BE LOOKING ME UP NOW.

10:29.697 --> 10:31.631
(laughs)
HE'S PROBABLY NOT.

10:31.631 --> 10:34.001
HEY, I JUST SIGNED
FOR THESE FLOWERS.

10:34.001 --> 10:37.504
UH, THEY'RE FROM SOMEONE
NAMED, UH, WAYNE--

10:37.504 --> 10:39.206
GET RID OF THEM.

10:39.206 --> 10:40.774
WHAT? WHAT?

10:40.774 --> 10:43.110
WHAT IS GOING ON?

10:46.379 --> 10:48.315
WHO ARE THE FLOWERS FOR?

10:48.315 --> 10:50.083
UM...

10:50.083 --> 10:51.351
ANGIE.

10:51.351 --> 10:54.722
OH, YEAH? WHY DOES IT SAY,
"REST IN PEACE"?

10:54.722 --> 10:56.656
HA! I WAS GOOD LAST NIGHT.

10:56.656 --> 10:58.892
