"IN LOVING MEMORY"?

11:01.261 --> 11:04.998
IN MEMORY OF THE LOVING.
ANY MORE QUESTIONS?

11:04.998 --> 11:07.534
YEAH, HOW MANY TIMES
ARE YOU GOING TO MENTION

11:07.534 --> 11:10.203
SLEEPING WITH MY DAUGHTER
BEFORE I LEAVE THE ROOM?

11:10.203 --> 11:14.007
LOOK, I'M SORRY. ALL RIGHT,
WE BOTH KNOW SHE'S AN ANGEL...

11:14.007 --> 11:17.745
TILL SHE WALKS UP
THOSE STAIRS. HELLO.

11:20.413 --> 11:21.915
COME ON, GEORGE.

11:21.915 --> 11:24.151
WHAT ARE THE FLOWERS
REALLY FOR?

11:24.151 --> 11:26.386
YOU GOT SOMETHING FOR WAYNE,
DIDN'T YOU?

11:26.386 --> 11:29.256
ALL RIGHT. YEAH,
THEY'RE FOR WAYNE'S FUNERAL.

11:29.256 --> 11:32.359
I'M GONNA TAKE 'EM
OVER THERE, YOU KNOW,

11:32.359 --> 11:35.062
'CAUSE I ALWAYS
KIND OF LIKED THE GUY.

11:35.062 --> 11:37.597
OH, MY GOD.
WAYNE IS DEAD?

11:37.597 --> 11:39.967
HE WAS JUST HERE
YESTERDAY.

11:41.769 --> 11:43.103
GOD, IT'S SO WEIRD,

11:43.103 --> 11:45.705
THE WAY YOU TOLD HIM
THAT BENNY'S DEAD,

11:45.705 --> 11:48.408
AND THEN THE NEXT DAY,
HE DIES?

11:48.408 --> 11:50.277
HOW DOES THAT HAPPEN?

11:50.277 --> 11:52.012
WAYNE WAS HERE?

11:52.012 --> 11:54.147
WHAT IS GOING ON, GEORGE?

11:54.147 --> 11:57.384
ALL RIGHT,
HERE IT IS, OKAY?

11:57.384 --> 11:59.920
WAYNE CAME TO SEE YOU.

11:59.920 --> 12:02.990
OKAY, MOM? HE KNEW...
THAT HE WAS DYING,

12:02.990 --> 12:07.727
AND HE WROTE DOWN
SOME LAST WORDS FOR YOU.

12:07.727 --> 12:10.363
"S-SORRY ABOUT EVERYTHING.

12:10.363 --> 12:11.965
"FORGET ABOUT ME.

12:11.965 --> 12:15.202
NEVER BLAME GEORGE."

12:15.202 --> 12:17.170
LET ME SEE THAT.

12:17.170 --> 12:18.972
IT CONTINUES.

12:18.972 --> 12:21.708
"I AM WRITING
IN DISAPPEARING INK

12:21.708 --> 12:24.411
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT
ANYONE TO..."

12:30.450 --> 12:33.020
IT'S GONE.

12:33.020 --> 12:37.190
NOW WE'LL NEVER KNOW!

12:47.134 --> 12:50.303
NOW YOU BETTER TELL ME
THE TRUTH ABOUT WAYNE.

12:50.303 --> 12:52.272
ALL RIGHT.
WAYNE WAS HERE YESTERDAY

12:52.272 --> 12:55.042
BECAUSE HE WANTED
TO SEE YOU, MOM.

12:55.042 --> 12:58.511
I TOLD HIM YOU WERE DEAD,
AND THESE FLOWERS ARE FOR YOU.

12:58.511 --> 13:00.313
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

13:00.313 --> 13:02.315
BECAUSE HE CHEATED
ON YOU ONCE,

13:02.315 --> 13:05.018
AND I DIDN'T WANT
TO SEE YOU GET HURT AGAIN,

13:05.018 --> 13:06.586
BECAUSE YOU'RE MY MOM.

13:06.586 --> 13:09.689
REALLY? WOW. THAT'S NICE,

13:09.689 --> 13:11.892
BUT IT'S A LIE.

13:11.892 --> 13:14.094
NOW TELL ME THE TRUTH...

13:14.094 --> 13:17.364
OR I'LL RIP OFF
ONE OF DUMBO'S EARS,

13:17.364 --> 13:20.567
AND HE'LL ONLY BE ABLE TO FLY
IN CIRCLES!

13:20.567 --> 13:22.435
OW. OW.

13:22.435 --> 13:24.004
TELL HER. TELL HER.

13:24.004 --> 13:26.339
THERE'S NOTHING TO TELL.

13:26.339 --> 13:28.808
(groans)
IT WAS ALL GEORGE'S IDEA!

13:28.808 --> 13:30.810
HE SET UP
THE WHOLE THING!

13:30.810 --> 13:32.379
OW!

13:32.379 --> 13:34.247
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT!

13:34.247 --> 13:35.849
OW!

13:35.849 --> 13:37.150
ALL RIGHT.
HERE'S WHAT HAPPENED,

13:37.150 --> 13:39.386
BUT JUST REMEMBER,
THIS IS THE '70s.

13:39.386 --> 13:42.589
"DISCO DUCK" WAS A HIT.
WHITE PEOPLE HAD AFROS, MOM.

13:42.589 --> 13:45.092
NOTHING MADE SENSE.

13:45.092 --> 13:47.360
(making whooshing sounds)

13:47.360 --> 13:49.529
HEY, GEORGE,
GEORGE, GEORGE,

13:49.529 --> 13:53.133
I GOT MY MOM'S BRA.

13:53.133 --> 13:55.135
BUT IF YOU HAVE THAT,

13:55.135 --> 13:58.138
WHERE'S SKIPPER
AND GILLIGAN SLEEPING?

13:58.138 --> 13:59.806
(Wayne and Benny
speaking indistinctly)

13:59.806 --> 14:01.141
THEY'RE COMING.

14:04.544 --> 14:06.479
(laughs)

14:06.479 --> 14:08.415
(laughs) STOP. OH.

14:08.415 --> 14:11.351
GEORGE,
TAKE YOUR GIRLFRIEND

14:11.351 --> 14:13.954
AND GO PLAY DOLLS
SOMEPLACE ELSE.

14:16.789 --> 14:18.625
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

14:18.625 --> 14:20.493
YOU FRAMED HIM.

14:20.493 --> 14:24.031
DO YOU REALIZE
BECAUSE OF WHAT YOU DID,

14:24.031 --> 14:27.267
I HATED MEN FOR 20 YEARS?

14:27.267 --> 14:28.768
HATED MEN?

14:28.768 --> 14:30.770
NOT ON FRIDAY
AND SATURDAY NIGHTS.

14:30.770 --> 14:32.572
HOW DUMB
DO YOU THINK I WAS?

14:32.572 --> 14:35.642
I KNEW THERE WASN'T
A GHOST IN YOUR ROOM.

14:35.642 --> 14:38.411
(imitating ghost moaning)

14:38.411 --> 14:39.779
AAH! OH!

14:39.779 --> 14:43.683
NO GHOST CALLS OUT
MEN'S NAMES.

14:43.683 --> 14:45.818
OH, NOW I GET IT!

14:45.818 --> 14:49.022
I NEVER UNDERSTOOD WHY A GHOST
WOULD HAUNT FOR TEN MINUTES,

14:49.022 --> 14:52.625
GO USE YOUR BATHROOM,
THEN HAUNT AGAIN.

14:55.228 --> 14:58.431
WAYNE WAS THE BEST THING
THAT EVER HAPPENED TO ME.

14:58.431 --> 15:00.934
I THOUGHT
WE WERE GONNA GET MARRIED.

15:00.934 --> 15:03.570
WHY WOULD YOU
DO SOMETHING LIKE THIS?

15:05.472 --> 15:07.941
WAYNE MAY HAVE BEEN
GREAT FOR YOU,

15:07.941 --> 15:09.742
BUT NOT FOR ME.

15:09.742 --> 15:11.611
WAS HE MEAN TO YOU?

15:11.611 --> 15:14.647
DID HE SMACK YOU AROUND
WHEN I WASN'T IN THE ROOM?

15:14.647 --> 15:18.318
BECAUSE THAT'S OKAY.
I GAVE HIM PERMISSION.

15:19.852 --> 15:22.022
IT WASN'T LIKE THAT.

15:24.124 --> 15:26.159
MOM, MOM, GUESS WHAT?

15:26.159 --> 15:28.996
THE COACH PICKED ME
TO BE ON THE ALL-STAR TEAM.

15:32.465 --> 15:33.866
OH, THAT'S GREAT.

15:33.866 --> 15:38.171
THAT MEANS YOU'RE BETTER
THAN ALL THE OTHER WATER BOYS.

15:38.171 --> 15:40.673
NO!
THE GAME IS SATURDAY NIGHT,

15:40.673 --> 15:44.377
AND YOU PROMISED YOU'D GO
IF I MADE THE TEAM.

15:44.377 --> 15:47.580
OKAY, QUIT YOUR WHINING.
I WILL BE THERE.

15:47.580 --> 15:48.815
(door opens)

15:48.815 --> 15:51.584
BABE? BABE?

15:51.584 --> 15:53.386
I GOT A BIG SURPRISE.

15:53.386 --> 15:55.855
GEORGE, GO TO YOUR ROOM.
TURN ON THE STEREO.

15:55.855 --> 15:57.357
NO, NO, NOT THAT.

15:57.357 --> 15:59.459
I MET
WITH THIS INVESTOR GUY.

15:59.459 --> 16:01.661
HE MAY WANT TO FRANCHISE
THE BUSINESS.

16:01.661 --> 16:04.664
I'M GONNA GO TO THE FONDUE PLACE
WITH HIM SATURDAY NIGHT,

16:04.664 --> 16:08.068
TRY TO SEAL THE DEAL.
BABE, I REALLY NEED YOU THERE.

16:08.068 --> 16:11.271
YOU CAN'T GO, MOM. YOU PROMISED
YOU'D BE AT MY ALL-STAR GAME.

16:11.271 --> 16:14.207
I KNOW,
BUT WAYNE NEEDS ME.

16:14.207 --> 16:17.277
UH, IF YOU REALLY
ARE AN ALL-STAR,

16:17.277 --> 16:19.312
YOU'LL MAKE THE TEAM
NEXT YEAR,

16:19.312 --> 16:23.650
AND I'LL--I'LL--I'LL GO
TO THAT GAME.

16:30.423 --> 16:33.793
YOU COULDN'T SHARE ME,
SO YOU RUINED MY LIFE?

16:33.793 --> 16:37.064
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT
WAYNE MEANT TO YOU, MOM.

16:37.064 --> 16:38.865
I WAS 10.
I DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING.

16:38.865 --> 16:41.901
I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE COOL
IF YOU MARRIED ELTON JOHN.

16:41.901 --> 16:43.470
OH.

16:43.470 --> 16:46.806
GEORGE, WAYNE COULD'VE MADE
OUR LIVES SO MUCH BETTER,

16:46.806 --> 16:48.508
BUT YOU BLEW IT.

16:48.508 --> 16:51.378
MOM, I FEEL HORRIBLE ABOUT THIS,
BUT THERE'S NOTHING I CAN DO.

16:51.378 --> 16:54.381
IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.
IT WASN'T A LONG TIME AGO.

16:54.381 --> 16:58.618
HE CAME BY THE OTHER DAY,
AND YOU TOLD HIM I WAS DEAD.

16:58.618 --> 17:00.019
YOU LIED.

17:00.019 --> 17:02.021
YOU'RE ALWAYS
CALLING ME A LIAR,

17:02.021 --> 17:04.057
BUT YOU ARE NO BETTER.

17:04.057 --> 17:06.593
YES, I AM.
I ONLY LIED ONCE.

17:06.593 --> 17:08.795
REALLY?
IS THIS THE FIRST TIME

17:08.795 --> 17:10.730
WAYNE TRIED
TO CONTACT ME?

17:10.730 --> 17:13.333
YES.

17:15.435 --> 17:18.138
HE COMES BY
EVERY TIME HE'S SINGLE.

17:18.138 --> 17:20.473
IT'S BEEN 7 TIMES
IN THE LAST 30 YEARS.

17:20.473 --> 17:24.611
OH,
HE MISSES YOU GREATLY.

17:24.611 --> 17:26.279
SEVEN TIMES?

17:26.279 --> 17:28.281
OKAY, SO I WAS RAISED

17:28.281 --> 17:31.318
BY THE BIGGEST LIAR
IN THE WORLD.

17:31.318 --> 17:34.354
YOU TOLD ME FOR MY BIRTHDAY
THAT YOU GOT ME A CAT,

17:34.354 --> 17:36.623
LIKE A SPECIAL BREED
CALLED THE "NUT-CAT."

17:36.623 --> 17:40.127
THAT SQUIRREL ALMOST
TORE UP MY WHOLE FACE.

17:40.127 --> 17:41.728
AT LEAST
I DIDN'T RUIN YOUR LIFE.

17:41.728 --> 17:43.930
I'M GONNA DIE ALONE,
THANKS TO YOU.

17:43.930 --> 17:46.065
NO, YOU'RE NOT, MOM,

17:46.065 --> 17:48.168
BECAUSE I'M GONNA FIND WAYNE,
AND I'M GONNA FIX THIS.

17:48.168 --> 17:51.504
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU GUYS
A SECOND CHANCE.
YOU TOLD HIM I WAS DEAD.

17:51.504 --> 17:54.274
SO I'LL TELL HIM THE TRUTH,
AND I PROMISE YOU, MOM,

17:54.274 --> 17:55.775
WHEN HE SEES YOU,
HE'S GONNA THINK

17:55.775 --> 17:58.778
YOU'RE AS BEAUTIFUL NOW
AS YOU WERE 30 YEARS AGO.

17:58.778 --> 18:02.182
OH, QUE LA, I'M LYING,
AND NOW I CAN'T STOP LYING.

18:10.190 --> 18:13.092
I TOLD YOU I'D FIX IT.

18:13.092 --> 18:14.394
WHAT'S GOING ON?

18:14.394 --> 18:16.095
I BROUGHT WAYNE HERE,

18:16.095 --> 18:19.699
AND HE WANTS TO CATCH UP,
REGENERATE LOVE.

18:19.699 --> 18:21.801
HELLO, BENITA.

18:21.801 --> 18:23.803
IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME.

18:23.803 --> 18:25.538
WAYNE.

18:25.538 --> 18:28.074
IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

18:28.074 --> 18:30.009
I'LL BE RIGHT OUT.

18:30.009 --> 18:33.045
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME
I WAS GONNA SEE HIM TONIGHT?

18:33.045 --> 18:36.749
JEEZ, I WOULD'VE WORN
MORE MAKEUP AND LESS UNDERWEAR.

18:36.749 --> 18:38.985
HEY, SHE'S WEARING
UNDERWEAR AGAIN.

18:38.985 --> 18:40.187
AY.

18:44.157 --> 18:49.329
OKAY,
THIS MIGHT WORK OUT.

18:49.329 --> 18:51.831
YEAH, I HOPE SO.
YOU KNOW, IT FEELS GOOD

18:51.831 --> 18:53.933
NOT HAVING THIS HANGING
OVER MY HEAD ANYMORE.

18:53.933 --> 18:56.336
WELL, IF YOU DON'T LIE
IN THE FIRST PLACE,

18:56.336 --> 18:58.505
THEN YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT HURTING PEOPLE.

18:58.505 --> 19:00.573
YOU KNOW,
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THAT.

19:00.573 --> 19:03.776
SOME LIES ARE ACTUALLY GOOD FOR
PEOPLE, LIKE YOU, FOR EXAMPLE.
DON'T TELL ME.

19:03.776 --> 19:07.447
NO, YOUR WEDDING RING.
YOU SHOULD KNOW.
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

19:07.447 --> 19:11.184
IF SOMEONE TRIES TO STEAL IT,
DON'T FIGHT FOR IT.

19:11.184 --> 19:14.554
SHOULD I FIGHT
FOR MY DIAMOND EARRINGS?

19:14.554 --> 19:17.324
ONLY IF THAT GUY'S SMALL.
DAMN IT.

19:20.193 --> 19:22.262
OHH!

19:22.262 --> 19:24.997
HEY,
WHAT DID HE SAY TO YOU?

19:24.997 --> 19:28.668
ALL THE RIGHT THINGS.
WE'RE GOING TO A MOTEL.
WHAT?!

19:28.668 --> 19:31.871
LOOK, I'M TRYING TO TAKE
THINGS SLOW THIS TIME.

19:31.871 --> 19:33.673
I'M GONNA SLEEP WITH HIM,

19:33.673 --> 19:35.675
BUT IF THINGS
DON'T WORK OUT,

19:35.675 --> 19:39.045
I DO NOT WANT HIM
TO KNOW WHERE I LIVE.

19:39.045 --> 19:41.781
I GOT A GOOD FEELING
ABOUT THIS!

19:41.781 --> 19:45.385
I FEEL BAD FOR THE PEOPLE
IN THE NEXT ROOM.

19:45.385 --> 19:47.387
THEY DON'T KNOW
THE MOTEL IS HAUNTED.

19:47.387 --> 19:50.022
(imitating ghost moaning)

19:50.022 --> 19:52.425
OH, WAYNE.
